---
title: Creamy Red Lentil, Veggie & Coconut Dhal with Basmati Rice & Yoghurt
description: Dhal is the ultimate bowl of goodness – rich in protein, a good source of fibre and full of aromatic flavours. The coconut cream balances the spices to create a meal that's both delectable and nourishing.

*Unfortunately, this week's tomato was in short supply, so we've replaced it with carrot. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
